  <brief_title>The Neuroprotective Effect of Lamotrigine and Interferon Beta 1a in Patients With Relapsing-Remitting Multiple Sclerosis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized, Placebo-Controlled Phase II Monocentric Trial for the Neuroprotective Effect of Lamotrigine Plus Interferon Beta 1a 30mcg Once Weekly Intramuscular in Patients With Relapsing-Remitting Multiple Sclerosis.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
