  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is designed to evaluate the neuroprotective effect of lamotrigine in the
      combination of interferon beta 1a once weekly intramuscular in patients with
      relapsing-remitting multiple sclerosis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
